collection_holder_name: Donald C. and Elizabeth M. Dickinson Research Center
pageContext.collection_title: John Rao Jr. Western Entertainers Collection, 1900-1972
pageContext.collection_description: Contains sound recordings and other print materials and memorabilia of western cowboys, including Gene Autry, Smiley Burnette, Jimmie Rodgers, Eddie Dean, Roy Rogers, Tom Mix, Allan "Rocky" Lane, Fuzzy Knight, Tex Ritter and others.
